    <br><br /><br>
    <p>(NAPS)&mdash;Springtime in California brings with it the season&rsquo;s bounty of fresh, local produce that inspires home and professional chefs alike. From salads to sandwiches, pastas to soups, it&rsquo;s pretty much a given that when a dish has &ldquo;California&rdquo; in its name, it&rsquo;s likely a dish made even better with delicious avocados.</p>
    <p>With premium California avocados at their peak, now is the perfect time to incorporate this delicious and nourishing fruit into any cuisine to give it that classic taste of the Golden State.</p>
    <br /><br />
    <table align="right">
